<div id="about-the-community" class="section-spacer">
    <h2 class="sect-title">About Erin Woods</h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Offering some of the most spectacular panoramic views of the City Downtown and the Canadian Rockies, the community in Erin Woods features abundant recreational options for its residents. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">The sprawling playing fields and immaculate greens render the Erin Woods Real estate, one of the most sought-after neighborhoods in the entire city. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Erin Woods feature a variety of different architectural styles that largely comprise single-family detached and attached units with the exception of a few apartment condos are sparingly strewn across the neighborhood. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">The average starting price of a typical detached unit in Erin Woods is $200,000, with the prices climbing higher for the more luxurious properties.</p>
        </div>
